name: Lost Pari$ (Not for sale)
description: Lost Pari$ was made after i had a weird dream today. The price is unbelievable high because i dont want you to buy this. Just read my story. My dream was about a young man walking the streets of Paris. Thousands of butterflies flew through the area. Statues suddenly appeared before him as a symbol of power. The voices of the statues told the man to get out of paris. This is how Lost Pari $ came about. It was a crazy dream through and through!
